text: Jeannie Carson (born Jean Shufflebottom; 23 May 1928) is a retired English- born comedian, actress, singer and dancer. She has a star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame. In 1956, Carson starred in her own series Hey, Jeannie!, which aired on CBS. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English stage actors Category:English voice actors Category:Actors from Yorkshire Category:English dancers Category:English singers
